### Telescope Base Theme

The main improvement in this update is that part of the Hubble theme's styles have now been split into their own theme, `telescope-theme-base`. 

The base theme contains all the boring stuff that you probably won't want to duplicate: the mobile navigation, forms, and basic styles for tables and other common elements. 

You can use it as a skeleton to build your own themes. To do so, simply remove the Hubble theme with `mrt remove telescope-theme-hubble`, create your own theme, and start styling!

Of course, you're also free to get rid of the base theme as well if you prefer customizing Telescope completely from scratch. 

