### Accounts Entry

I also finally got rid of the ugly default account popup and replaced it with the [accounts-entry](https://github.com/Differential/accounts-entry/) package. 

### Tracking Votes

Finally, Telescope now tracks your upvotes and downvotes and displays your upvotes on your user profile page. 

